’Ů@c62dddf0b30d062c869b76badc22e0419ec4b5060c0d4eaf97cbfb4a01b65e38ŮŐTitle: title: clear
Path: Examples
Content:
Clear the terminal.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> clear


```
Clear the terminal but not its scrollback history.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> clear --keep-scrollback


```
’Ů@484edee8e6cebb79be89cbb88fe92bfa48dc615709b81d0e4ac34f735bf922a1ŮtTitle: title: clear
Path: Notes
Content:
By default clears the current screen and the off-screen scrollback buffer.
